For my drive wheel feedforward controlled by Kraken, I need to configure meters per second on SysID. For feedback, I should select rotations per second. Additionally, to utilize the Ks, Ka, and Kv values, I can create a simple motor and replace the feedforward values with a new instance of SimpleMotorFeedforward configured with driveKS, driveKV, and driveKA. This requires two lines of code:
```csharp
SimpleMotorFeedforward feedforward = new SimpleMotorFeedforward(driveKS, driveKV, driveKA);
swerveDrive.replaceSwerveModuleFeedforward(feedforward);
```
